<section class="guide-panel" data-page="echo">
  <header class="panel-header">
    <span class="eyebrow">Echo</span>
    <h2>Sets et priorit&eacute;s de stats</h2>
  </header>

  <div class="echo-shell">
    <div class="echo-sets">
      <article class="echo-set echo-set--best">
        <div class="echo-set__header">
          <div class="echo-set__title">
            <img src="../../assets/img/set/Law%20of%20Harmony.png" alt="Loi de l'harmonie" />
            <div>
              <span class="echo-choice-label">Choix recommand&eacute;</span>
              <h3>Loi de l'harmonie (3p) + 2p flexible</h3>
              <p>
                Le socle le plus propre pour garder de bons d&eacute;g&acirc;ts perso tout en donnant jusqu'&agrave;
                <span class="accent-value">+16% DGT de Comp&eacute;tence d'&Eacute;cho</span> &agrave; l'&eacute;quipe.
                Le 2p le plus simple reste <span class="accent-value">P&egrave;lerinage au vent</span>.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="echo-item-grid">
          <article class="echo-item echo-item--primary">
            <img src="../../assets/img/echo/Reminiscence%20Fenrico.png" alt="R&eacute;sidu r&eacute;sonnant : Fenrico" />
            <div>
              <span class="echo-item__label echo-item__label--primary">&Eacute;cho recommand&eacute;</span>
              <h4>R&eacute;sidu r&eacute;sonnant : Fenrico</h4>
              <p>
                Le meilleur choix standard : bonus Aero et Attaque lourde, exactement ce que sa rotation exploite le mieux.
              </p>
            </div>
          </article>

          <article class="echo-item echo-item--secondary">
            <img src="../../assets/img/echo/Bell-Borne%20Geochelone.png" alt="Tortue clochante" />
            <div>
              <span class="echo-item__label">Alternative support</span>
              <h4>Tortue clochante</h4>
              <p>
                &Agrave; consid&eacute;rer surtout dans des versions plus support, par exemple avec Phrolova + Cantarella.
              </p>
            </div>
          </article>
        </div>
      </article>

      <article class="echo-set echo-set--alt">
        <div class="echo-set__header">
          <div class="echo-set__title">
            <img src="../../assets/img/set/Moonlit%20Clouds.png" alt="Nuages lunaires" />
            <div>
              <span class="echo-choice-label echo-choice-label--alt">Alternative cibl&eacute;e</span>
              <h3>Nuages lunaires (5p)</h3>
              <p>
                La version la plus buff mono-carry, avec <span class="accent-value">+22,5% ATQ</span> apr&egrave;s l'Outro.
                &Agrave; viser surtout avec <span class="accent-value">Galbrena + Shorekeeper</span>.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="echo-item-grid">
          <article class="echo-item">
            <img src="../../assets/img/echo/Impermanence%20Heron.png" alt="H&eacute;ron impermanent" />
            <div>
              <span class="echo-item__label">&Eacute;cho associ&eacute;</span>
              <h4>H&eacute;ron impermanent</h4>
              <p>
                Le compagnon naturel du 5p Nuages lunaires pour un swap propre, plus de buff et un peu d'&eacute;nergie.
              </p>
            </div>
          </article>
        </div>
      </article>
    </div>

    <section class="echo-mainstats">
      <div class="echo-mainstats__header">
        <span class="echo-mainstats__kicker">Meilleures stats d'&Eacute;cho</span>
        <h3>Configuration 4 / 3 / 3 / 1 / 1</h3>
        <p>
          Commence par verrouiller le double 3 co&ucirc;t Aero. Les substats servent surtout &agrave; lisser la ligne CRIT et un peu de Recharge.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="echo-mainstats__grid">
        <article class="mainstat-card">
          <span class="mainstat-card__slot">4 co&ucirc;t</span>
          <div class="mainstat-card__stats">
            <span class="mainstat-primary">DGT CRIT</span>
            <span class="mainstat-sep">&gt;</span>
            <span class="mainstat-alt">Taux CRIT</span>
          </div>
          <p>Choisis surtout selon l'&eacute;quilibre de ta ligne CRIT.</p>
        </article>

        <article class="mainstat-card mainstat-card--priority">
          <span class="mainstat-card__slot">3 co&ucirc;t</span>
          <div class="mainstat-card__stats">
            <span class="mainstat-primary">DGT Aero</span>
          </div>
          <p>Le premier 3 co&ucirc;t Aero est la base du build.</p>
        </article>

        <article class="mainstat-card">
          <span class="mainstat-card__slot">3 co&ucirc;t</span>
          <div class="mainstat-card__stats">
            <span class="mainstat-primary">DGT Aero</span>
            <span class="mainstat-sep">&gt;</span>
            <span class="mainstat-alt">ATQ%</span>
          </div>
          <p>Le double Aero reste le choix standard. Aero + ATQ% reste jouable si besoin.</p>
        </article>

        <article class="mainstat-card">
          <span class="mainstat-card__slot">1 co&ucirc;t</span>
          <div class="mainstat-card__stats">
            <span class="mainstat-primary">ATQ%</span>
          </div>
          <p>Le premier 1 co&ucirc;t fixe la base offensive du build.</p>
        </article>

        <article class="mainstat-card">
          <span class="mainstat-card__slot">1 co&ucirc;t</span>
          <div class="mainstat-card__stats">
            <span class="mainstat-primary">ATQ%</span>
          </div>
          <p>Le second 1 co&ucirc;t ATQ% garde le profil simple et coh&eacute;rent.</p>
        </article>
      </div>

      <div class="echo-substats-divider">
        <span>Substats prioritaires</span>
      </div>

      <div class="substats-grid substats-grid--single">
        <article class="substat-card">
          <h4>Ordre recommand&eacute;</h4>
          <p>
            <span class="accent-text">Recharge</span> jusqu'au confort
            &gt; <span class="accent-text">Taux CRIT</span>
            = <span class="accent-text">DGT CRIT</span>
            &gt; <span class="accent-text">ATQ%</span>
            &gt; <span class="accent-text">DGT Attaque lourde%</span>
            &gt; <span class="accent-text">ATQ</span>
          </p>
        </article>
      </div>
    </section>
  </div>
</section>
